  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Senior IT Recruiter",
  "description": "<p>Are you passionate about connecting people with the right opportunities? Do you have a keen eye for talent and the drive to succeed in a fast-paced environment? If you’re ready to grow in the world of IT recruitment, we want to hear from you!</p>\n<h3><u><strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong></u></h3>\n<p>✅ <strong>Learn &amp; Lead</strong> – Understand job requirements and work closely with hiring managers.<br>\n✅ <strong>Source Top Talent</strong> – Hunt for candidates via LinkedIn, job portals, and networking events.<br>\n✅ <strong>Screen &amp; Assess</strong> – Identify the best candidates and conduct qualification interviews.<br>\n✅ <strong>Negotiate &amp; Close</strong> – Support candidates through salary discussions and job offers.<br>\n✅ <strong>Ensure Smooth Onboarding</strong> – Help new hires transition seamlessly into their roles.<br>\n✅ <strong>Track &amp; Report</strong> – Stay organized and keep hiring managers updated on recruitment activity.</p>\n<h3><u><strong>What You Bring</strong></u></h3>\n<p>🔹 <strong>Education:</strong> Bachelor or Diploma<br>\n🔹 <strong>Experience:</strong> 5+ years in recruitment or talent acquisition (in IT roles is a plus!)<br>\n🔹 <strong>Skills:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Strong communication (written &amp; verbal)</li>\n  <li>Solid negotiation abilities</li>\n  <li>Goal-driven and able to perform under pressure</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in Microsoft Office (Word, Excel, PowerPoint)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><u><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></u></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>A dynamic and supportive team to help you grow your career</li>\n  <li>Hands-on experience in IT recruitment with exciting hiring projects</li>\n  <li>Opportunities to develop your sourcing, negotiation, and hiring strategy skills</li>\n</ul>",
